msgctxt "sn56.52:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.52:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "6. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.52:0.3"
msgid "52. Pokkharaṇīsutta "
msgstr "52. A Lotus Pond "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn56.52:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, pokkharaṇī paññāsayojanāni āyāmena, paññāsayojanāni vitthārena, paññāsayojanāni ubbedhena, puṇṇā udakassa samatittikā kākapeyyā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose there was a lotus pond that was fifty leagues long, fifty leagues wide, and fifty leagues deep, full to the brim so a crow could drink from it. "

msgctxt "sn56.52:1.2"
msgid "Tato puriso kusaggena udakaṃ uddhareyya. "
msgstr "Then a person would pick up some water on the tip of a blade of grass. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.52:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.52:1.4"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yaṃ vā kusaggena ubbhataṃ, yaṃ vā pokkharaṇiyā udakan”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the water on the tip of the blade of grass, or the water in the lotus pond?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.52:1.5"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ—pokkharaṇiyā udakaṃ; appamattakaṃ kusaggena udakaṃ ubbhataṃ. "
msgstr "“Sir, the water in the lotus pond is certainly more. The water on the tip of a blade of grass is tiny. "

msgctxt "sn56.52:1.6"
msgid "Saṅkhampi na upeti, upanidhampi na upeti, kalabhāgampi na upeti pokkharaṇiyā udakaṃ upanidhāya kusaggena udakaṃ ubbhatan”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the water in the lotus pond, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s not even a fraction.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.52:1.7"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa … pe … "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.52:1.8"
msgid "yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.52:1.9"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

